Review Title: Great lunch choice in Vincom Centre, ask for Phat 👍
Review Text: Lovely little restaurant in the Vincom Centre, food is delicious and the lime, lemongrass and ginger juice is the best! Very reasonable pricing, and the staff, especially Phat, are so helpful, attentive and polite. Thoroughly recommended for a linch while exploring District 1 HCMC 👍

Review Title: semplice ristorante, solo roll giaì pronti o da farsi su misura, eccellente
Review Text: semplice ristorante nella food area all'interno del Vincom mall , tutto servito a roll gia' preparati o da farsi a misura, ottimo ed economico

Additional Ratings:
Giá trị: 5
Dịch vụ: 5
Đồ ăn: 5
Không khí: 5
Review Text: i came here for dinner on 1 Dec when i had a nine days trip to HCM last year.it was the second time i had meal at Wrap and Roll. the  first time was year 2017 ,that time i think i had meal at their Nguyen Hue street branch,but i cant find it from their website. so i went to vincom center store.besides having dinner,i can do shopping here also.i ordered bun rieu cua cha (rice noodles with crab paste and pork), xoi ga la dua (pandan sticky rice with chicken), banh cuon nhan thit (steamed rice rolls with minced pirk and mushroom) and cafe nuoc cot dua (iced coffee with coconut milk). all are delicious,i had rice noodles soup before, i think the taste here is nice, a bit sour and sweet.pandan sticky rice with chicken is yummy,a combination of dessert and chicken meat, very special. and the steamed rice rolls not a heavy meal, i can have many plates of it. love the rolls, a bit like cantonese cheon fun.coffee is ok, sweet. the menu here is big, and many food i want to try, but i have one stomach only, so will come next time .the place is quite big, but very busy, i think it is popular among both locals and tourists.so if want to come here, better avoid peak hours.

Review Title: At the time thought a good option
Review Text: Lots of staff members, hanging around. I asked for napkins they only gave enough for each person.  I asked again, and I said can I have one napkin and they actually only brought one napkin. Food was ok, pancake was oily. I feel overpriced for the portions.

Additional Ratings:
Giá trị: 4
Dịch vụ: 4
Đồ ăn: 3
Review Text: Very reasonable, simple vietnamese food. I had their grilled pork and noodle salad, the shrimp spring rolls, and the grilled chicken spring rolls. The service was very quick. Each of the spring rolls came with a different sauce that complemented the roll well. The noodle salad was a bit on the smaller side (only half the bowl was filled) but otherwise was not bad. Only odd thing was that they charged me for using the napkin in the end.

Review Title: Simple, good for an everyday light lunch
Review Text:
Wanted to try dry Pho type of dish.
Can be a dish you don't get tired of.
Not the best quality, but acceptable, the Pho noodles were less sticky than i thought (i prefer a bit of elasticity).
Dipping sauce was really good.

I was many time visiting the outlets of wraps & rolls In different locations in Vietnam 
Love it. Easy to eat and taste so fresh

Review Text:
restaurant "Wrap and Roll" propose une cuisine vietnamienne, avec beaucoup de choix. Le service est efficace et rapide ,produits frais
je recommande pour un repas sur le pouce

Review Title: 気軽に入れるチェーン店ですね
Review Text:
以前から気になっていて今回のホーチミン旅で初めて利用しました。
ホーチミン市内にはあちこちありました。
メニューは写真付きなので言葉が通じなくても大丈夫です。
なんとかオーダーし、ちょっと実物と写真が違いましたがそこは我慢（笑）
ベトナム飯を(名前は忘れてしまいました)頂く事が出来ました。
手軽に味わえるので良いと思いますよ。
Thư giãn, như không đông đúc, ngon như tự làm, vừa đúng cỡ bữa ăn, giá cả phải chăng, sạc cho di động, WiFi. Khá sạch sẽ. Bạn cần gì nữa?

Review Title: Bữa ăn nhẹ tốt với các thành phần sạch đáng tin cậy
Review Text: Chúng tôi đã gọi rau, bọc bọ cánh cứng, bánh tráng và tất cả các thực phẩm có hương vị sạch và tươi! Tôi muốn giới thiệu nơi này cho bất cứ ai thật nhanh chóng và dễ dàng :)

ホーチミン市で何箇所か見つけました。チェーン店ですし店内もキレイなので、
旅行者でも入りやすいと思います。メニューも写真付きで英語も添えられている点も良かったです。
若いベトナム人のカップルが多かったような気がします。地元でも人気なんでしょうね。
Surtaxe de 3euros à la fin du repas. On nous a donné des lingettes qui se sont avérées payantes... Service très moyen, pas du tout aimable.

Additional Ratings:

Review Title: 고수를 싫어 하는 사람도 먹을 수 있는 체인점
Review Text:
고수를 싫어 하는 사람도 막을 수 있는 체인점 입니다. 
가격은 대략 1사람에 만원 정도면 배부르게 먹을 수 있습니다. 
전체적으로 맛 있다기 보다는 무안한 편 입니다.
昼間に行きました。とても綺麗なお店です。清潔感溢れたお店です。料理もとても美味しかったです。飲み物も色んなソフトドリンクありました。

泊まっているホテルの近くだったので
よるご飯に利用しました☆
春巻きとフォーが美味しかったです。

ただ、ビールの333が品切れだったので
バドワイザーを頼んだら
冷えている物がなくて
グラスに氷を入れて持ってきました。
ビールに氷！？って
ちょっとビックリでした笑

日本人のお客さんがチラホラ。
ツアーの外人さんも多く、賑わってました。

二人でビール1杯ずつと
料理3品でお腹いっぱいでしたが
1700円くらいでお手軽です♡
Thức ăn rất ổn và không khí dễ chịu. Các nhân viên đều hữu ích và cho phép thời gian để chúng tôi quyết định.

ベトナムの色んな、春巻きが食べれるのは、もちろん、パインセオも美味しく！
中々です、ホーチンミンでもあちこちにありますが、気軽に入れて、いいのではないかと。

Review Text: 在河內嘗過一次以為是小店，後來在胡志明市見到，原來是連鎖店。非常越南特色，也有很多不同款的春卷。套餐更抵！

小腹がすいて入りました。
生春巻きはこの旅で食べてなかったので注文。他にバインセオとフォーを油で揚げて肉野菜あんかけをかけた、かた焼きそば風の料理を。フォーを揚げたものは軽めのお餅のようで、あんかけも牛肉と野菜でオイスターソースが効いていて美味しかったです。
生春巻きはやっぱり乾いてて(´-`)ちょっと硬かった〜

Review Title: good healthy and delicious vietnamese food and price is not that expensive !
Review Text:
Just chance upon this restaurant after searching so many restaurants  that night
in the main avenue.

We just feast on their springrolls, hotpot and local beers, then asked for the receipt and surprise to see that its not so expensive.

You can check on their menu the price and selections if you 
prefer combination of their specialties.

No wonder there are many yuppies and millenials in this 
restaurant !
Mプラザ内にある店舗にて。チェーン店のようでグエン・フエ通りにもある。春巻きが有名だけど、ベトナム料理は一通り揃っている。

정통 월남쌈을 즐길 수 있습니다.
가격도 합리적이라 좋습니다.
맛도 괜찮고 분위기도 나쁘지 않습니다.
베트남 로컬 식당으로는 최고 같습니다.

My Wrap And Roll meal was at M Plaza. Not listed. Had a tray with lots of goodies. Wife had the Pho Like soup. Great flan dessert with soy and matcha. Unusual drinks. To eat here you must be a semi veg and willing to put your steak and fries away.
